Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.30,0:00:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在被星光照射的頂屋裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.90,0:00:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獨自一人聆聽著天空的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.55,0:00:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用玻璃的繃帶遮住眼睛行走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是孤獨的馬戲團孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.85,0:00:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤身一人的悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,震動的繃帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.87,0:00:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撼動著心靈……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.35,0:01:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用溫柔的眼神期待與某人的相會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.05,0:01:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我耳邊細語「請留在我身邊」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.27,0:01:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Silent Voice
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.43,0:01:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都不知道殖民地會掉落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.03,0:01:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因為聯邦高官\n只顧著自己逃命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.24,0:01:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都柏林的人都來不及逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.54,0:01:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加拉帕用奧特穆拉\n又能救多少人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.44,0:01:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殖民地掉下,加美尤也目睹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.01,0:02:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十六話 重力下的波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.17,0:02:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉,伊萊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.74,0:02:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.38,0:02:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這混亂中還能遇上真好運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.24,0:02:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.38,0:02:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太慢了,急速下降\n已經在做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.87,0:02:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可怕,好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.64,0:03:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,檢查損害程度!\n是,各船員檢查損害程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.82,0:03:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臭哈曼,毫不在乎人命\n視野開始清晰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.69,0:03:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掉落殖民地的策略看起來是成功了\n馬士文這次可驕傲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.48,0:03:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣我古利明可要失勢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.57,0:03:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要利用此機會擊沉亞加瑪\n打倒ZZ高達來挽回名聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.02,0:03:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殖民地就這樣豎起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.08,0:04:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?人聲?恐懼,悲傷之聲?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.18,0:04:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟做這樣過份的事\n這麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.55,0:04:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若想找出戰鬥的理由\n這就是你的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.60,0:04:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這聲音是..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.86,0:04:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天是好日子哩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.69,0:04:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這混帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.78,0:04:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有罪的人全死了\n為何這麼做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.23,0:04:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼氣勢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.28,0:04:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.62,0:05:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸運的女神\n一定會對我古利明微笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.11,0:05:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醒來吧,波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.92,0:05:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,怎麼了?\n有一陣寒意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.77,0:05:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還在發燒,我幫你敷毛巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.23,0:05:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對,剛才的感覺不是\n不可以,現在是重要時期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.58,0:05:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生病非休息不可,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.32,0:05:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是有討厭的東西來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.97,0:05:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有討厭的東西要來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.20,0:06:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有討厭的東西要來?加美尤?\n不,是波蕾嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.70,0:06:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也成為這廢堆中的一部份吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.56,0:06:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這和普通MS不同\n你真礙事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.10,0:06:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這力量是?\n像你這種人不可原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.16,0:06:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃走了\n要搜索大家回亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.85,0:06:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世 波蕾茲二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.36,0:06:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可能感覺有重力,不是在宇宙\n對,現在在地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.56,0:06:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經睡了多久?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.82,0:06:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為目前處境還不用找我出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.17,0:06:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假使這樣,我們就不需要人就像波蕾二世一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.58,0:07:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是,處境還不是太差\n可以使我們轉向有利條件的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.80,0:07:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你才要我醒來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.22,0:07:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當戰爭時,有一些人都知道強化人\n這各戰爭有助於我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.51,0:07:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假如解開強化人,就會使情勢轉變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.61,0:07:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒用的說法都是沒用的,古利明\n波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.48,0:07:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假使你要處於優勢,說要清除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.29,0:07:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我將幫助你,假使我們破壞亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.38,0:07:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我使用精神武器對付他們就足夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.40,0:07:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不再等了,亞加瑪起航吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.47,0:07:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.00,0:07:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和奧特穆拉連絡\n高達隊行蹤不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.22,0:07:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都柏林應該還有殘存者\n亞加瑪向都伯林前進   是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.02,0:08:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,波蕾你在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.23,0:08:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非去不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.31,0:08:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏\n在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.73,0:08:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洗達,帶我去MS處\n你非休息不可阿,波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.48,0:08:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.96,0:08:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪有危險阿\n咦?亞加瑪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.82,0:08:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若我能登上邱被雷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.55,0:08:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點重\n是上手駕駛者的感覺嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.83,0:08:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾茲\n什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.01,0:08:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桑多拉就此前往基巴撒爾\n和哈曼大人會合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.90,0:08:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.97,0:08:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會擊沉亞加瑪\n作為守信送給哈曼大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.35,0:08:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託了,波蕾茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.63,0:09:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.28,0:09:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事但這核戰機不能飛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.57,0:09:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個也是,在那樣的衝擊下\n大家能平安也算好運了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.05,0:09:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度和亞加瑪有沒有事呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.23,0:09:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將核戰機丟下走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.50,0:09:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓杜雷斯檢查吧\n艾莉,伊萊來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.47,0:09:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點,再留在這裏很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.94,0:09:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是奧特穆拉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.89,0:09:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏面應該有很多避難者\n去吧,露卡  知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.74,0:09:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何亞加瑪會有危險?\n有東西要來這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.24,0:09:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是要擊沉亞加瑪而來的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.93,0:10:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是緊急發射\n所以威力剩下一半也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.96,0:10:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊\n美加炮對焦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.14,0:10:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目標是?\n能看見嗎?波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.83,0:10:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再右點,再右點\n發射焦點向右   是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.42,0:10:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概13度,停\n停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.05,0:10:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在上點,4度\n在上4度   是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.16,0:10:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裏\n停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.19,0:10:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看不見目標\n對準目標   是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.11,0:10:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就要來了,來了,趁現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.44,0:10:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美加炮發射!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.98,0:10:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道\n螢幕放至最大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.07,0:10:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,貫穿了殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.64,0:10:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那確實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.12,0:10:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是精神力的高達MK2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.86,0:10:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,精神力高達?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.19,0:10:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,波蕾!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.50,0:11:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真好大膽,亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.30,0:11:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,精神力高達來了\n防衛泡在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.22,0:11:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,右邊發射飛彈\n全力反擊,發射美加炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要注滿能量需要時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.52,0:11:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼亞加瑪好像早有防備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.21,0:11:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.91,0:11:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MS用艙門開啟了\n是你們開的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.30,0:11:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.11,0:11:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邱貝雷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.26,0:11:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰駕駛解體中的丘貝雷?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.52,0:11:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓亞加瑪被擊沉也不要緊嗎?\n丘貝雷是我的..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.01,0:11:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪的MS現在才出擊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.90,0:11:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.42,0:12:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧特穆拉,奧特穆拉請回答\n不行,沒回應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.30,0:12:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧特穆拉的航道漸漸下降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.99,0:12:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧特穆拉的控制室\n發生了什麼事?完全不能通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.82,0:12:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難民還坐著吧\n比查,靠近那各控制室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.70,0:12:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡你聽見嗎?去制止奧特穆拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.02,0:12:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒別的辦法,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.35,0:12:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速度配合點,降下\n知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.98,0:12:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在不動會被吹走的,Z高達找人按著\n找人到控制室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.69,0:12:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道,但從哪裏進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.65,0:12:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,那裏\n逃生口?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.12,0:13:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,右邊動不了,若由前面進攻不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.64,0:13:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這感覺是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.92,0:13:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,避開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.20,0:13:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這感覺是什麼?\n這種陰暗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.22,0:13:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,試試吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.40,0:13:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙為何...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.47,0:13:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做同樣的事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.49,0:13:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓人不愉快,消失吧\n休想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.61,0:14:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用激光器當做盾牌?\n為何這傢伙會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.02,0:14:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部被破壞了?那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.98,0:14:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼,真煩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.38,0:14:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何知道我所想的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.34,0:14:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我想說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.51,0:14:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何以這種MS\n敵對精神力高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.46,0:14:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人不高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.89,0:14:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不高興就回宇宙去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.33,0:14:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就此結束你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.48,0:14:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,射中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.79,0:14:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度..!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.54,0:14:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何出來了?會死的,離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.92,0:14:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題\n小心那駕駛員跟我很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.40,0:15:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是新人類嗎..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.22,0:15:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是ZZ高達?\n真有趣,ZZ高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.48,0:15:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.86,0:15:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高達?這是..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.78,0:15:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是精神力的高達MK2\n精神力?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.72,0:15:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼感覺?\n波蕾快回亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.13,0:15:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\n它是我的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.44,0:15:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊還差一點點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.91,0:15:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,成功了,伊萊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.52,0:15:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊\n伊萊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.70,0:16:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艙門鈕是這個嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.09,0:16:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.48,0:16:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艙門開了\n進去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.11,0:16:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MS回來了,只有一艘嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.72,0:16:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在你們之中有加拉帕的人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.89,0:16:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全乘MS出去了\n你是聯邦的人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.76,0:16:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看就知道吧,那加拉帕的人\n只有控制是那些?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.86,0:16:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.24,0:16:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在精神力的高達面前躲藏\n也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.34,0:16:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行阿,怎麼辦?捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.45,0:16:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追逐戰到此為止\n受死吧,ZZ高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好了,能量快要耗盡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.66,0:17:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.24,0:17:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了\n結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.93,0:17:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我抓到你了,ZZ高達,覺悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.74,0:17:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.73,0:17:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與奧特穆拉的通訊接上了\n什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.16,0:17:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是奧特穆拉\n難民平安,我們會盡力駕駛奧特穆拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.27,0:18:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,去接回奧特穆拉\n全速前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.47,0:18:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,精神力的高達呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.82,0:18:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達,竟然沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.38,0:18:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿..激光劍沒能量了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.09,0:18:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.22,0:18:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾\n捷度,我知道精神力高達駕駛員是誰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.78,0:18:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?你知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.80,0:18:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是你嗎?這令人不高興的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.69,0:18:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不高興是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.09,0:18:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?你想說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.01,0:18:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.22,0:19:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人看見自己本身當然會不高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.57,0:19:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但怎樣不高興,怎樣憎恨也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.13,0:19:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也殺不了 制止不了自己本身的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.59,0:19:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼?\n我就是你,你就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.20,0:19:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你極度厭惡我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.94,0:19:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是愛羅比.波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.61,0:19:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是波蕾茲,我是波蕾茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.63,0:19:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我啊,去死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.51,0:19:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還活著嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.68,0:19:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,精神力高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.19,0:20:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.33,0:20:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.28,0:20:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…你…你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.74,0:20:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再ZZ高達的意識中有波蕾在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.38,0:20:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想逃嗎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.18,0:21:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的是波蕾\n波蕾明明被殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.82,0:21:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這場戰爭雖說不上是大勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.79,0:21:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但救出都柏林人民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.73,0:21:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也值得安慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.65,0:21:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那現在為犧牲的人們默哀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.64,0:22:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全員志哀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.57,0:22:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黑色的雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.30,0:22:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成百 成萬 上億的繁星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.49,0:22:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何只是閃耀而已 展示你言語的能力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.55,0:23:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我也能不回頭地 讓心靈出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.70,0:23:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若能把多如繁星的生命儲存的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.65,0:23:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把整個銀河也化作光芒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.35,0:23:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,化作緊握在掌心的 生命的重量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.32,0:23:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我仍未能看見宇宙的路標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.22,0:23:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手掌觸摸著一千萬年的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.37,0:23:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼回宇宙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.76,0:23:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也從北國的卡拉巴基地回宇宙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.67,0:23:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是為了潛入哈曼所在的SIDE 3並和新的戰艦會合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.39,0:24:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但 那裏有新的女戰士在等著我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.93,0:24:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集 高達ZZ 擬·亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.69,0:24:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連馬士文都…？

